{"updated_at": "2012-03-27T06:40:48Z", "repo": "rails", "created_at": "2012-03-27T06:40:48Z", "owner": "rails", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/comments/4710858", "id": 4710858, "issue_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/5606", "issue_id": 5606, "user": {"repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/teohm/repos", "type": "User", "html_url": "https://github.com/teohm", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/teohm/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/teohm/subscriptions", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/teohm/following{/other_user}", "gravatar_id": "37ef5e5ddd4b05465000dbea5d4b22e2", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/teohm/orgs", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/teohm", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/teohm/gists{/gist_id}", "avatar_url": "https://0.gravatar.com/avatar/37ef5e5ddd4b05465000dbea5d4b22e2?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2F4cef360eb538876a560f897552b0ce8a.png", "id": 164703, "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/teohm/events{/privacy}", "login": "teohm", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/teohm/received_events", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/teohm/followers"}, "body": "FYI, it only happens for multipart form because this is what Rack returns to Rails:\r\n\r\n```ruby\r\n{ \"I\\xC3\\xB1t\\xC3\\xABrn\\xC3\\xA2ti\\xC3\\xB4n\\xC3\\xA0liz\\xC3\\xA6ti\\xC3\\xB8n_name\" =>   \r\n  \"I\\xC3\\xB1t\\xC3\\xABrn\\xC3\\xA2ti\\xC3\\xB4n\\xC3\\xA0liz\\xC3\\xA6ti\\xC3\\xB8n_value\" }\r\n```\r\nand in Rails, `ActionDispatch::Http::Parameters#encode_params` decided to only encode param value, but not param name. As a result we got:\r\n\r\n```ruby \r\n{ \"I\\xC3\\xB1t\\xC3\\xABrn\\xC3\\xA2ti\\xC3\\xB4n\\xC3\\xA0liz\\xC3\\xA6ti\\xC3\\xB8n_name\" =>\r\n  \"I\u00f1t\u00ebrn\u00e2ti\u00f4n\u00e0liz\u00e6ti\u00f8n_value\" }\r\n```\r\n\r\nHope this helps to clarify the root cause.", "_id": {"$oid": "523eb55ebd354364b90120ec"}, "html_url": "https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/5606#issuecomment-4710858"}
